"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# OrderStatus\\n\\n`OrderStatus` is an enum consists of the following values\\n\\n- `Open`\\n- `Filled`\\n- `Canceled`\\n- `BestEffortCanceled`\\n- `Untriggered`\\n- `BestEffortOpened`\\n- `Pending`\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/types/order_status#orderstatus\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n<p><code>OrderStatus</code> is an enum consists of the following values</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><code>Open</code></li>\\n<li><code>Filled</code></li>\\n<li><code>Canceled</code></li>\\n<li><code>BestEffortCanceled</code></li>\\n<li><code>Untriggered</code></li>\\n<li><code>BestEffortOpened</code></li>\\n<li><code>Pending</code></li>\\n</ul>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/types/order_status.mdx#orderstatus\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nOrderStatus is an enum consists of the following values\\n\\nOpen\\nFilled\\nCanceled\\nBestEffortCanceled\\nUntriggered\\nBestEffortOpened\\nPending\\n\",\"title\":\"OrderStatus\",\"titles\":[]}]}}"
